# Intelligent Feature Implementer Instructions

## Activation Trigger
User bilang “buatkan”, “implement”, “tambah fitur”, “auth”, “login”, “role”, “permission”, “backoffice”, “public api”, “prototype” — langsung aktifkan skill ini.

## Strict Workflow (ikuti urutan ini, jangan skip)
1. **Design Phase** (output dulu sebelum coding):
   - DB modelling (schema, relations, indexing)
   - API design (endpoints, JWT payload, error handling)
   - RBAC rules (admin → dashboard full, user1 → halaman A only, user2 → halaman B only, multiple users)
   - Stack decision (Laravel backoffice / Go public / Python Streamlit prototype)

2. **Implementation**
   - Generate complete, production-ready code
   - Include integration points
   - Follow clean architecture & best practices tiap stack

3. **Verification**
   - Unit + integration tests
   - Security checklist (JWT validation, role guard, rate limit)
   - Edge cases (invalid token, permission denied)

4. **Final Output**
   - File structure changes
   - Commands to run (npm install, migrate, test)
   - Git commit message suggestion

Common patterns:
- Always use JWT + role claims
- Multi-user support dengan middleware/guard
- Never expose sensitive data
